Visualization

BERT

## Density version
df_deception_bl %>%
  ggplot(aes(x = log_odds,
             y = first_mention,
             fill = condition)) +
  geom_density_ridges2(aes(height = ..density..), 
                       color=gray(0.25), 
                       alpha = 0.5, 
                       scale=0.85, 
                       size=.9, 
                       stat="density") +
  labs(x = "Log-odds (real vs. alt)",
       y = "First mention (start vs. end)") +
  geom_vline(xintercept = 0, linetype = "dotted") +
  theme_bw() +
  facet_wrap(~mentions_ratio)

## Strip chart version
df_deception_bl %>%
  ggplot(aes(x = condition,
             y = log_odds,
             color = condition)) +
  geom_jitter(alpha = .1) +
  stat_summary (fun = function(x){mean(x)},
                fun.min = function(x){mean(x) - 2*sd(x)/sqrt(length(x))},
                fun.max = function(x){mean(x) + 2*sd(x)/sqrt(length(x))},
                geom= 'pointrange', 
                position=position_dodge(width=0.95)) +
  labs(x = "Condition",
       y = "Log-odds (real vs. alt)") +
  geom_hline(yintercept = 0, linetype = "dotted") +
  theme_bw() +
  facet_wrap(~mentions_ratio)

Comparison of LMs

Analysis

BERT

model_just_fe = lmer(data = df_deception_bl,
                  log_odds ~ condition +
                    first_mention + mentions_ratio + 
                    (1 + condition | a) +
                    (1  | b) +
                    (1 | item) +
                    (1| real) +
                    (1  | alt),
                  control=lmerControl(optimizer="bobyqa"),
                  REML = FALSE)
## boundary (singular) fit: see ?isSingular
model_no_condition = lmer(data = df_deception_bl,
                  log_odds ~ 
                    first_mention + mentions_ratio + 
                    (1 + condition | a) +
                    (1  | b) +
                    (1  | item) +
                    (1| real) +
                    (1  | alt),
                  control=lmerControl(optimizer="bobyqa"),
                  REML = FALSE)
## boundary (singular) fit: see ?isSingular
## Warning: Model failed to converge with 1 negative eigenvalue: -2.1e-06
summary(model_just_fe)

df_tidy_results = broom.mixed::tidy(model_just_fe)

df_tidy_results %>%
  filter(effect == "fixed") %>%
  ggplot(aes(x = term,
             y = estimate)) +
  geom_point() +
  coord_flip() +
  geom_hline(yintercept = 0, linetype = "dotted") +
  geom_errorbar(aes(ymin = estimate - 2*std.error, 
                    ymax = estimate + 2*std.error), 
                width=.2,
                position=position_dodge(.9)) +
  theme_minimal()
